Womz Storage Manager WSM
Author: Eric Wamsley
Site: http://ewams.net

Summary
WSM aims to provide a simple utility for managing storage devices on a Linux system.

Details
WSM is a Perl program that uses common built-in features of an OS to manage storage devices in a Linux system.

Features
Scan for new storage devices
View storage devices and device details
Automatically install S.M.A.R.T tools (smartmontools) and RAID tools (mdadm) if desired

TODO
